casebody.data: Appeal of WILLIAM J. CONLEN. Docket No. 815. Submitted January 28, 1925; decided January 31, 1925. William J. Conlen, the taxpayer, in his own behalf. Willis D. Nance, Esq. (Nelson T. Hartson, Solicitor of Internal Revenue) for the Commissioner. Before Grattpner, Lansdon, Littleton, and Smith. [NO OPINION]
